function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)


	idNageedClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(NPC_Nageed, true)
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idNageedClone) then
		
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idNageedClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idNageedClone, loc_NageedWalkTo, "NPC_Walk", false)
		Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idNageedClone, 1.0)
				
	end
	
end
